    <item>
      <title>折扣后苹果3月份中国iPhone出货量猛增12%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/apple-s-china-iphone-shipments-soar-12-in-march-after-discounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[官方数据显示，在苹果公司及其零售商大幅降价后，3 月份中国 iPhone 出货量猛增约 12%，这表明遏制销量加速下滑的努力正在取得初步成果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/apple-s-china-iphone-shipments-soar-12-in-march-after-discounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 08:09:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Reddit 在第一份收益报告中大放异彩，股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/reddit-reports-sales-topping-estimates-in-first-report-since-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Reddit Inc. 的股价在盘前交易中上涨了 16%，此前该社交媒体平台广告系统的改进帮助推动季度销售额高于其作为上市公司的首次业绩预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/reddit-reports-sales-topping-estimates-in-first-report-since-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 20:14:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
